{"tid":1427921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年輕人，夠唔夠膽搞一次 ”核彈也不割” 大遊行？","createTime":"2019-08-07T08:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T11:45:25.000Z","uid":267881,"like":45,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"af9bf6f00c58f5b8be281b917cf881fc3a2816d1","tid":1427921,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"只準三十歲以上、十二歳以下參與<br />\n<br />\n著黑色街坊裝或深色西裝<br />\n<br />\n鼓勵以各行各界做單位參與<br />\n<br />\n只有少量年輕人在場做義工<br />\n<br />\n全港停止勇武一天，和理飛全面進場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你地仍然相信民意企係我地呢邊<br />\n<br />\n如果你地夠膽勇於面對民意<br />\n<br />\n就光明正大反駁對家：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再屈學生搞亂香港<br />\n係全香港人一條心對抗暴政</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年輕人在遊行終點表達衷心感激"},{"pid":"583b47099c59f45fb764e573d1c91cbb77faea62","tid":1427921,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"唔好再俾敵人扣呢頂帽子"},{"pid":"ac99b02625fe337c3bbfb14a8f9d3402a857ee2f","tid":1427921,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:26:07.000Z","msg":"同埋要謙卑地請佢地俾意見同批評，以示對支持者嘅尊重"},{"pid":"98424d22e86f5aa47f623319fff47fe26ac34773","tid":1427921,"uid":100230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"30以上年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3b6eab8f6d97fa58ea02ce0638b8de4c0038d3","tid":1427921,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"呢步棋對林鄭黎講係核彈級"},{"pid":"cb490f52eb21bb127d4ef2d704178cdc876dd8aa","tid":1427921,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98424d22e86f5aa47f623319fff47fe26ac34773","tid":1427921,"uid":100230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:30:33.000Z","msg":"30以上年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T08:32:35.000Z","msg":"年輕人負責做搞手邀請其他年齡層參加"},{"pid":"e19a6823e415b797c7acd1e27f50